name: HEN WavyPunk #53 GOGOs Tribute (Limited Edition)
description:
WavyPunks are 1/1 3D Voxel Heads that are made to be worn on your Avatars in Cryptovoxels.

Exclusively designed & created by artist 1OF1NEO

** This Limited Edition (HEN WavyPunk #53) is a tribute to The GOGOs Project by @gogoporen & @0x00000010! **

This NFT will included a Vox (Wearable) Airdropped to your Wallet
